member": {"username": "jasondennis12139", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c0d156bdc802ad1e5b7890e903e620d8?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jasondennis12139", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1606876692, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c0d156bdc802ad1e5b7890e903e620d8?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c0d156bdc802ad1e5b7890e903e620d8?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 521719}, "last_reply_by": "Sunnic", "last_touched": 1629912522, "title": "才上班一个月就让签竞业了？怎么破？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/797832", "created": 1629853633, "content": "本科毕业，校招刚刚入职一个月\r\n入职的时候明确说只签保密不签竞业\r\n现在突然要求我们签竞业协议\r\n条款大概是 2 年竞业，百分之 30 的补偿金\r\n具体哪些公司不能去由公司根据业务情况而定，包括但不限于华为中兴海康小米\r\n违约赔偿金 5 年工资\r\n\r\n我刚毕业啥都不会也要让我签竞业？还全公司就要求新员工签？\r\n这玩意怎么破？", "content_rendered": "<p>本科毕业，校招刚刚入职一个月\n入职的时候明确说只签保密不签竞业\n现在突然要求我们签竞业协议\n条款大概是 2 年竞业，百分之 30 的补偿金\n具体哪些公司不能去由公司根据业务情况而定，包括但不限于华为中兴海康小米\n违约赔偿金 5 年工资</p>\n<p>我刚毕业啥都不会也要让我签竞业？还全公司就要求新员工签？\n这玩意怎么破？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1629858252, "replies": 64, "id": 797832}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7504/adad/881_large.png?m=1579006017", "name": "vue", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7504/adad/881_normal.png?m=1579006017", "title": "Vue.js", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/vue", "topics": 714, "footer": "", "header": "The Progressive JavaScript Framework", "title_alternative": "Vue.js", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7504/adad/881_mini.png?m=1579006017", "stars": 996, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 881, "parent_node_name": "js"}, "member": {"username": "sxox", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a88e/dc1c/542626_mini.png?m=1629859906", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sxox", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1618474483, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a88e/dc1c/542