商品房的房价是 8000+，而且我也只是在县城周边，骑电动车去县城也就 15 ~ 20 分钟。\n对此我在网上查了相关资料，都说这种基建拆迁补偿的很少，而且可以强拆，补这么少的钱，这不是明抢吗？目前只是听村长说，真正的补偿方案也还没有公布，还没有正式的相关文件和谈判，我是提前了解一下相关的情况，想问一下有没有遇到相关事情的朋友，或者你们的亲朋好友有遇到相关的事情的，谢谢大家</p>\n", "last_modified": 1629860360, "replies": 58, "id": 797852}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1583044904", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1583044904", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 2178, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904", "stars": 727, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "CyberShadiao", "website": "", "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e42d/2358/528583_mini.png?m=1615600227", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/CyberShadiao", "tagline": "", "twitter": null, "created": 1610765246, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e42d/2358/528583_mini.png?m=1615600227", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e42d/2358/528583_mini.png?m=1615600227", "location": "", "btc": null, "id": 528583}, "last_reply_by": "hanqian", "last_touched": 1629917406, "title": "电脑现在有必要装安全软件吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/797866", "created": 1629859838, "content": "平时电脑只用来写下代码，看看视频，下一些绿色版的工具。之前没用火绒前一些激活工具 windows defender 总是会报毒，然后就下了个火绒，接管了 windows defender 。", "content_rendered": "平时电脑只用来写下代码，看看视频，下一些绿色版的工具。之前没用火绒前一些激活工具 windows defender 总是会报毒，然后就下了个火绒，接管了 windows defender 。", "last_modified": 1629859838, "replies": 56, "id": 797866}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1593747127", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1593747127", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 971, "footer": "", "head